n-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":947,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/07\/24\/best-sadaqah-rich-independent\/","url_meta":{"origin":2033,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Best charity is given when independent, enriched","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"The best charity is what you give when you are independent; start by spending on your dependents.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1426 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15548,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/05\/charity-upper-hand-better\/","url_meta":{"origin":2033,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Giving charity is better than receiving it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe upper hand is better than the lower hand.\u00a0The upper hand is one that gives and the lower hand is one that takes.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1429, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u